3324.Name: Beacon Hill Club Men's PTI 10+
3324.Details:
Sunday 11/14/21

Matches will begin at 8:30am at clubs in the Summit, NJ area. Draw size will remain at 16 teams. 

Cost to enter is $120 per team. This includes lunch, water/gatorade, beer and prizes for winners are runners up. All matches will count towards PTI. Main draw matches will be full 3 set matches, all backdraw matches will be 2 sets, and a super tiebreak in lieu of a 3rd set. 

Please contact Greg Morgan, gmorgan@beaconhillclub.org if you have any questions.
3324.RegistrationDetails:
To be eligible for this event, your team average PTI must not be lower than 10. For example a team consisting of Player A- PTI 5 and Player B- PTI 15 has an average PTI of 10 and is allowed to play. 

A Team with Player A 8 PTI and Player B PTI- 11 has an average PTI of 9.5 and is not eligible for this event.
